{"type": "article", "id": 23667, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-11T08:24:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 24754, "name": "Anglepoise®"}, {"id": 24755, "name": "Knots Studio"}, {"id": 24756, "name": "Primo Toys"}, {"id": 24757, "name": "Typical Organization"}, {"id": 24302, "name": "Alexander Lervik"}, {"id": 24758, "name": "Invasione Creativa"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702112452DUy38IKO2bNXvFWo.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Tingest 2016 Collection by Alexander Lervik</h2>\n<p>这是瑞典品牌 Tingest 推出的 2016 年新款手表，他们称灵感源于芭蕾舞裙的薄纱。表盘上覆盖了一面带孔的圆盘，指针在下面形成了填色块，看起来有点朦胧。设计师故意让圆点分布地较为随意，不会让圆孔本身变得紧张。手表使用日本石英机芯，表带是摩洛哥革，产品目前还没有上市。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110400tpwAgscizFuJ3kbI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110401TxA4UGKNgifejR58.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110401CTxnuYivbBLqwV28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110403nKal4eGQvoMt3Dyz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110403bh5dIxDcuB4UvgFS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>PANTONE bookcase by Invasione Creativa</h2>\n<p>这是一组置物盒的概念设计，它是一个带抽屉的方框。方框和抽屉都是白色的，只在后面填充以不同的颜色，在整齐有序中带着一点活泼。方框本身是一个书架，它与书本、光碟、茶杯等带有装饰感的东西放在一起，组成有互动感的装饰。可以挂在墙上或罗列在地上，设计者是三位来自意大利的设计师，产品还是一个概念。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110404oLYejmBJvDsxAut6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110404ni17gThRwIGK2SXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62638889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110405ZhXNMzVU1ClnrdoG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62638889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110405tvr6odR9uAK7gObI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62638889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110406O9Z3jVxQCUIFgLAf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62638889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Original 1227™ by Anglepoise® </h2>\n<p>Anglepoise® 台灯是 1930 年代生产的一款经典台灯，它拥有一个折叠灯壁和一段弹簧连接，有一种俏皮的工业感，你可以在皮克斯动画片片头看到。这盏台灯至今仍在小批量生产并有无数衍生版本。Anglepoise® 最近推出了可用于户外的铰链式壁灯 Original 1227™，可以选择多种型号，预计 6 月份可出售，售价 180 英镑起，<a href=\"https://www.anglepoise.com/product/original-1227-mini-wall-mounted-lamp\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071104068fWZvydUBuNQTxJi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110407Ie47LYu5hUPT6dnW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110409cZ45ICaNty8w0SlW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110409BHjVZ6K8FATL1irs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<h2>spunky seating by Knots Studio </h2>\n<p>这组打结的软垫让人不由自主想躺在上面，以色列的工作室 Knots Studio 使用了木质圆环将它捆扎起来，并做成不同型号和亮丽的颜色，让它变得非常活泼。另有一款安装了木腿作为凳子，型号较小的有 45 厘米宽，更适合儿童，售价 110 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/269396971/medium-dark-blue-white-stripes-cushion?ref=shop_home_active_1\">这里是购买链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110410OmtsHJo9fCIM47cQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110411caxN9o2EuKtCURYS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110412167dVI52mO0Are4p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071104129BDOdcGsQzhPke3a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.43166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110413qNbsyEAjtcTHWh0M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Cubetto by Primo Toys </h2>\n<p>这是英国伦敦的开发团队 Primo 设计的编程积木盒，是该团队推出的最新款。它包括一个立方体机器人 Cubetto，一块编程板，16 个彩色的按钮，一张世界地图和一本故事书。4 种彩色按钮分别指示向前、向左、向右和功能函数，按照特定的顺序排列就能指示机器人达到地图上的一个位置，以此来锻炼小朋友的逻辑思维能力，产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/primotoys/cubetto-hands-on-coding-for-girls-and-boys-aged-3?token=e3978e14\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110414WZYLKq3mgwu0ito9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71556122\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110414EqdSigZ73mWUIGzC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071104153dPnIDFlUBbZAOmc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110416GbRtIQek9F2u6NCz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110416CjPILTqfVpltYivx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>New Tea Ceremony by Typical Organization</h2>\n<p>这组茶叶包装的亮点在配色，相互之间区分度很高且有很强的撞击感，比如绿色配橙色，红色配蓝色，新鲜而潮流。每个包装上都是一个带吸管的茶杯图案，用不同的颜色突出吸管，引起人们喝的欲望。整体包装上都有排列整齐的黑色圆点，增加了年轻和潮流的气息。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110417HnrfmWJTIYboh6VK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110417rnEwhcZWglaJdBoI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110418TiBo6uCYy8avq194.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110419JBCaV8TM6iEK7ch5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}